10  How python code is executed
    The code is compiled into bytecode and this code is converted by the Python
        virtual machine into machine code.
    If you use the java based version of python(jython) it compiles the python 
        code into java bytecode then to machine code.
    To be clear you import java code into the jython code (not the jython into the java??) 	
	
