8   For loops
    The basic for loop in python has this syntax: "for some_counter_name in range(how_many_times):'
	Range cn also include these values:'range(starting_index, ending_index_isn't_included, increment_by)'

*******************************************************************************
9  For..else
   Use the'break' statement to break out of a loop early.
   You can add an 'else' statement to your for that executes only if the for loop executes completely without early termination.       

